quran[24]{c,v,t}:
  12,53,"Futhi angizibizi ngokhululekile ngempela umphefumulo uholela ebubini ngaphandle uma ibe nomusa iNkosi yami, ngempela iNkosi yami ingethethelelayo inesihawu"
  12,54,"Futhi iNkosi yathi, “mletheni kumina ngizozikhethela yena mina” ngakho-ke kwathi lapho seyikhuluma naye yathi “ngempela wena namhlanje usezingeni eliphezulu elithembekile”"
  12,55,"(UJosefa waphendula) wathi, “ngibeke esikhundleni sokuba ngibe umlondolozi wezinqolobana zezwe ngempela mina ngizoba ngumlondolozi onolwazi”"
  12,56,"Futhi kanjalo-ke sambeka ezingeni eliphezulu uJosefa emhlabeni ukuthi ahlale kuwona noma ngabe ikuphi lapho ethanda khona, sehlisela umusa wethu phezu kwanoma ngabe ubani esimthandayo futhi asiwulahli umvuzo wabenzi bokuhle"
  12,57,Futhi ngempela umvuzo wempilo ezayo ungcono kulabo abakholwayo futhi abamesabayo (uMvelinqangi)
  12,58,Futhi abafowabo kaJosefa bafika bangena kuyena ngakho-ke wayebazi (ukuthi bangabafowabo) kepha bona bengasamboni (ukuthi unguJosefa)
  12,59,"Futhi kwathi lapho esebalungisela umhlinzeko wabo (ukudla ababezokuthenga) wayesethi, “yizani kumina nomfowenu ozalwa nguyihlo aniboni yini ukuthi mina ngenza isilinganiso esigcwele nokuthi mina ngingumamukeli wezihambeli ongcono kunabanye na?”"
  12,60,Kepha uma ningezi naye kumina angeke nize nisithole isilinganiso (esigcwele sokudla) kumina futhi angeke nize nisondele kumina
  12,61,"Bathi, “sizozama ukuthi uyise amdedele futhi ngempela thina sizokwenza lokho”"
  12,62,(UJosefa) wayesethi ezincekwini zakhe “fakani imali yabo emithwalweni yabo uma sebehamba ukuze bayibone uma sebephindele emndenini wakubo ukuze babuyele emumva”
  12,63,Ngakho-ke kwathi lapho sebephindele emumva kubaba wabo bathi “Oh Baba wethu! Senqatshelwe isilinganiso (sokudla) ngakho-ke thumela kanye nathi umfowethu ukuze sinikezwe isilinganiso (sokudla) futhi ngempela thina sizomlondoloza”
  12,64,"(Uyise) wathi, “ngakube nginganethemba yini ngaye njengendlela enganethemba ngayo ngomfowabo ngaphambilini na? Ngakho-ke uMvelinqangi ungumlondolozi ongcono futhi yena ungonomusa ngokwedlulele ukwedlula abanomusa”"
  12,65,"Futhi kwathi lapho sebevula imithwalo yabo bathola ukuthi imali yabo iphindiselwe emumva kubona bathi, “Oh Baba wethu! yini enye esingayifisa na? Lena imali yethu ibuyiselwe kuthina futhi kufanele sithole ukudla komndeni wethu futhi silondoloze umfowethu futhi sandise isilinganiso somthwalo wekameli, lokho kuyisilinganiso esilula”"
  12,66,"(Uyise) wathi, “angisoze neze ngamthumela kanye nani kuze kube ninginika isithembiso (isifungo) ngoMvelinqangi ukuthi nizombuyisela kumina ngaphandle uma nizungelezwe (izitha)” ngakho-ke kwathi lapho sebemnikile isithembiso sabo (isifungo ukuthi bazobuya naye) wathi “uMvelinqangi ungufakazi kulokhu esikushoyo”"
  12,67,"Futhi (ubaba wabo) wathi, “Oh Madodana ami! ningangeni esangweni elilodwa ngenani emasangweni ehlukene futhi angeke nginisize ngalutho kuMvelinqangi, ukwehlulela akusikhona kwamuntu ngaphandle kokuthi kungokukaMvelinqangi ngethembele kuyena futhi ikuyena lapho bethembela khona abanethemba”"
  12,68,Futhi kwathi lapho sebengenile njengoba babephoqwe ubaba wabo akubasizanga ngalutho maqondana noMvelinqangi ngaphandle kwesidingo emphefumulweni kaJakobe eseneliseka futhi ngempela yena wayenalo ulwazi lwalokhu esamfundisa kona kepha iningi labantu alazi
  12,69,Futhi kwathi lapho sebengena kuJosefa wamhlalisa kanye naye umfowabo(Benjamin) wathi“ngempelaminangingumfowenu ngakho-ke ungaphatheki kabi ngenxa yalokho abakwenzayo”
  12,70,Ngakho-ke kwathi lapho esebalungiselela umthwalo wabo wafaka isitsha sokuphuza emthwalweni kamfowabo sabe sesiyamemeza isimemezi (sathi) “Oh nina zihambi! ngempela ningamasela”
  12,71,Baphendukela kubona bathi “kungabe yini enilahlekele na?”
  12,72,Bathi “silahlekelwe isitsha seNkosi futhi lowo ozosiletha (sona) uzothola (okulingene) nomthwalo wekameli futhi mina ngiyazibophezela kukona”
  12,73,Bathi “Sifubga ngoMvelinqangi ngempela benazi ukuthi asizanga ukuzokwenza ukona ezweni futhi asiwona amasela”
  12,74,Bathi “ngakho-ke siyini isijeziso uma kungukuthi ningabaqambi manga na?”
  12,75,Bathi “inhlawulo yako ukuthi lowo esizotholakala emthwalweni wakhe (isitsha) yena uqobo uzoba inhlawulo yako kanjalo sibanika umvuzo abayizoni”
  12,76,"Ngakho-ke waqala (ngokusesha) imithwalo yabo ngaphambi kokuba (aseshe) umthwalo womfowabo wayesesikhipha (isitsha senkosi) emthwalweni kamfowabo samenzela kanjalo icebo uJosefa, wayengeke amthathe umfowabo ngokwenkolo (ngokomthetho) wenkosi ngaphandle uma uMvelinqangi ethanda, siyawenyusa amazinga kulowo esimthandayo nangaphezulu kwabo bonke abanolwazi (kepha uMvelinqangi) unolwazi"